When we first saw the orphanage in Imuris, Mexico, we knew we had to do something. 

With the help of our friends, we took 30 kids living in a 1 bath 2 bedroom house into 13 bedrooms and we also rescued this dog named Imuris.🐶

It was an amazing experience taking care of these children, who were so happy and grateful to be able to live in a bigger area. 

A house full of love! 🥰 🙏🏻
